data.description: Do you want to own your own piece of Texas paradise? This is place is for you! This 3 bed 2 bath home sits on 10 acres and comes with its own shooting range, pool, large workshop or RV shed, and two storage sheds. This property is set up for horses or livestock of your choice. Inside you will find country living at its finest with a wood accents through out the home. The kitchen has granite countertops, a copper sink and rock backsplash. There are two propane fireplaces inside the home. The primary retreat is very spacious. The primary ensuite has granite counter tops and a copper sink enhanced with a beautiful multi-colored wooden wall accent. There is a covered patio great for enjoying afternoon tea and watching the beautiful West Texas sunsets.
